snippet.description:

The most awaited Wedding Video of the year is here , Enjoy this Shadi Season with this üéâüòç

Available in 5 fruity flavours üçπ

This Video shows all the crazy fun that happens in Big Fat Indian weddings. Indias and wedding season madness . Brides going on crazy diets to loose weight before Marriage , the morning after wedding and playing shadi rasam games with new bhahi and bhaiya like kagna games , Pre Bridal functions like mata ki choki , cocktail , sanjeet , roka , sagai , god tika , struggles of love marriage , cousins and best friends planning bachelorette for bride of the group , haldi ceremony and bhai behen getting emotional , Relatives giving advices about marriage. All the money , gifts , wedding preps , indian food , gol gappe , tikki , chart items , Paneer Tikka ,  spicy food , indian sweets , shaadi lehenga , bride makeup , wedding shopping , crazy dancing on wedding songs . Indian aunties taking lime light . Mehendi functions getting henna done and celebrating with family , friends , cousins . Ldki Wale vs ladke Wale , wedding photographers , pharo time and shadi wali coffee and crying on bidai , attending Big Fat Indian weddings like Kohli Tents , Flying Drones in weddings , Grand , Indian Bride entry with russians arounds , Wide variety of Indian Wedding Tasty food , malai chaap to gulab jamun , jalebi rabri , ice cream , Kids wearing skivi sweater under lehenga to deal with winter weddings , the struggles of Rishta before Marraige , Dealing with dowry , Every Girls struugles , Indian mom and super excited for daughter wedding , dreaming about grandchidlren , her beti being a maa one day , buying and placing a lot indian snacks daal kachori , samosa , pakore , dry fruits & nuts , barati ready for baraat dance on dhol , tired from 7 days of shadi functions , haldi , cocktail , sangeet , god tikka , mehendi , god bharai , halwai at home , indian relatives and theri demands , exclusive parlour makeup , hd bridal makeup , celebrity makeup , airbrush makeup , glitter makeup , high wedding makeup and hairstyle prices , wonder ladies with babies in wedding and doing rasams , dealing traffic jam while reaching a shaadi , every girls efforts of getting in lehenga , jhumka , doing makeup and then getting out of lehenga , removing heavy layers of makeup before sleeping , removing jwelery bangles , high heels , going on honeymoon and celebrating New Year goa , newyork , paris , london , switerland , enjoying bhaji , mathi achar , bondi ladoo , with tea or masala Chai , Going to Chandi Chowk for bridal shopping , choosing from wide variety of Bride lehenga color choices , red , maroon , pink , blue , green , trying different designs sabyasachi , manish malhotra , celebrity bridal lehengas , lehenga from jaipur with heavy embroidery work , crazy lehenga shopkeppers , high prices of lehenga and bargaining in that , bride not able to diet near marraige eating outside food golgappe to curb with full day of wedding shopping , after wedding counting money got from shagun , decorating gold daimond jewelry in front of indian guest buidling new homes before marraige , saas bahu happy in their new mother daughter relationship , kids mesmerized by new bhabhi and her makeup kit . 
This video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in an indian wedding.  
Relish and Relive your Memories.. You will have major nostalgia .

snippet.title: How To Train Your Dragon | Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
How To Train Your Dragon - In Theaters June 13

From three-time Oscar¬Æ nominee and Golden Globe winner Dean DeBlois, the creative visionary behind DreamWorks Animation‚Äôs acclaimed How to Train Your Dragon trilogy, comes a stunning live-action reimagining of the film that launched the beloved franchise. 
On the rugged isle of Berk, where Vikings and dragons have been bitter enemies for generations, Hiccup (Mason Thames; The Black Phone, For All Mankind) stands apart. The inventive yet overlooked son of Chief Stoick the Vast (Gerard Butler, reprising his voice role from the animated franchise), Hiccup defies centuries of tradition when he befriends Toothless, a feared Night Fury dragon. Their unlikely bond reveals the true nature of dragons, challenging the very foundations of Viking society. 

With the fierce and ambitious Astrid (BAFTA nominee Nico Parker; Dumbo, The Last of Us) and the village‚Äôs quirky blacksmith Gobber (Nick Frost; Snow White and the Huntsman, Shaun of the Dead) by his side, Hiccup confronts a world torn by fear and misunderstanding. 
As an ancient threat emerges, endangering both Vikings and dragons, Hiccup‚Äôs friendship with Toothless becomes the key to forging a new future. Together, they must navigate the delicate path toward peace, soaring beyond the boundaries of their worlds and redefining what it means to be a hero and a leader. 

The film also stars Julian Dennison (Deadpool 2), Gabriel Howell (Bodies), Bronwyn James (Wicked), Harry Trevaldwyn (Smothered), Ruth Codd (The Midnight Club), BAFTA nominee Peter Serafinowicz (Guardians of the Galaxy) and Murray McArthur (Game of Thrones).
How to Train Your Dragon is written, produced and directed by DeBlois. It is also produced by three-time Oscar¬Æ nominee Marc Platt (Wicked, La La Land) and Emmy winner Adam Siegel (Drive, 2 Guns). How To Train Your Dragon is part of the Filmed For IMAX¬Æ Program, which offers filmmakers IMAX¬Æ technology to help them deliver the most immersive movie experience to audiences around the world. 

Inspired by Cressida Cowell‚Äôs New York Times bestselling book series, DreamWorks Animation‚Äôs How to Train Your Dragon franchise has captivated global audiences, earning four Academy Award¬Æ nominations and grossing more than $1.6 billion at the global box-office. Now, through cutting-edge visual effects, DeBlois transforms his beloved animated saga into a breathtaking live-action spectacle, bringing the epic adventures of Hiccup and Toothless to life with jaw-dropping realism as they discover the true meaning of friendship, courage and destiny.

YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@UniversalPictures¬†

snippet.title: TURKEY FRY | Vaan Kozhi Varuval | Traditional Village Style Turkey Fry Recipe | Vaan Kozhi Uppu Kari
snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we cook spicy turkey fry recipe using the traditional method. We cook village-style turkey recipe using fewer ingredients, mainly shallots, dried chili, cold-pressed gingelly oil, and more.

We call this recipe Vaan Kozhi Uppu Kari, Vaan Kozhi Varuval.

The taste is spicy.

snippet.title: Shiv Sena Vs Shiv Sena Me Kiski Jeet? ft. Medha | Mumbai Elections | Jist
snippet.description:
In the run-up to the Maharashtra Assembly elections, JIST reporter Medha dives into the political nerve of Mumbai. This election season is unique, with two factions each of Shiv Sena (Uddhav Thackeray vs. Eknath Shinde) and NCP (Sharad Pawar vs. Ajit Pawar) battling it out. The BJP stands strong with the Mahayuti alliance, while the Congress remains a crucial part of the Maha Vikas Aghadi.

Medha travels across Mumbai, covering its two key divisions‚ÄîMumbai Suburban and Mumbai City‚Äîvisiting critical constituencies to gauge the mood of the voters. From alliances to political rivalries, and voters revealing their preferences, get an on-ground view of who could shape the future of Mumbai.

Watch now to discover what Mumbai's people are thinking about this high-stakes election!

snippet.title: A Minecraft Movie | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready to craft your world. #MinecraftMovie - only in theaters 2025.

From Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures and starring Jason Momoa and Jack Black, ‚ÄúA Minecraft Movie,‚Äù directed by Jared Hess, is the first-ever big screen, live-action adaptation of Minecraft, the best-selling video game of all time.  

The film also stars Emma Myers (‚ÄúWednesday‚Äù), Oscar nominee Danielle Brooks (‚ÄúThe Color Purple‚Äù), Sebastian Eugene Hansen (‚ÄúJust Mercy, ‚ÄúLisey‚Äôs Story‚Äù), with Jennifer Coolidge.

Welcome to the world of Minecraft, where creativity doesn‚Äôt just help you craft, it‚Äôs essential to one‚Äôs survival!  Four misfits‚ÄîGarrett ‚ÄúThe Garbage Man‚Äù Garrison (Momoa), Henry (Hansen), Natalie (Myers) and Dawn (Brooks)‚Äîfind themselves struggling with ordinary problems when they are suddenly pulled through a mysterious portal into the Overworld: a bizarre, cubic wonderland that thrives on imagination.  To get back home, they‚Äôll have to master this world (and protect it from evil things like Piglins and Zombies, too) while embarking on a magical quest with an unexpected, expert crafter, Steve (Black).  Together, their adventure will challenge all five to be bold and to reconnect with the qualities that make each of them uniquely creative‚Ä¶the very skills they need to thrive back in the real world. 

Oscar nominee Hess (‚ÄúNinety-Five Senses,‚Äù ‚ÄúNacho Libre‚Äù) directed, with Roy Lee, Jon Berg, Mary Parent, Cale Boyter, Jason Momoa, Jill Messick, Torfi Frans Olafsson and Vu Bui producing, and Todd Hallowell, Kayleen Walters, Brian Mendoza, Jonathan Spaihts, Pete Chiappetta, Andrew Lary and Anthony Tittanegro executive producing.

The director‚Äôs creative team behind the camera includes BAFTA-nominated director of photography Enrique Chediak (‚Äú127 Hours,‚Äù ‚ÄúTransformers: Rise of the Beasts‚Äù), Oscar-winning production designer Grant Major (‚ÄúThe Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Meg‚Äù), editor James Thomas (‚ÄúPok√©mon: Detective Pikachu‚Äù, the ‚ÄúBorat‚Äù films), Oscar-winning VFX supervisor Dan Lemmon (‚ÄúThe Jungle Book,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù), and costume designer Amanda Neale (‚ÄúThe Meg,‚Äù ‚ÄúWhat We Do in the Shadows‚Äù).  Casting is by Rachel Tenner.  The music supervisors are Gabe Hilfer and Karyn Rachtman, and the music is by Mark Mothersbaugh (‚ÄúThor: Ragnarok,‚Äù the ‚ÄúLEGO¬Æ‚Äù movies).

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present A Vertigo Entertainment/On The Roam/Moj√§ng Aktiebolag Production, A Jared Hess Film, ‚ÄúA Minecraft Movie.‚Äù  The film will be distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures worldwide and by Legendary East in China, and released only in theaters and IMAX in North America on April 4, 2025, and internationally beginning 2 April 2025.

snippet.title: Paardarshi | Lashcurry | MTV Hustle 4
snippet.description:
The first imagery of life that you see‚Ä¶ is your home and your people. So today, I‚Äôm going to show you the things around my life‚Ä¶ the things I‚Äôve witnessed while growing from Vinayak to Lashcurry.

Song Credits

Track Name: Paardarshi
Written & Performed By: Lashcurry
Music Producer: Aditya Pushkarna
Primary Artist: Lashcurry
Track Name: Paardarshi
Singer/Performed By/Cast: Lashcurry
Lyricist/Written By: Lashcurry
Music Produced By: Aditya Pushkarna
Co-Composer: Aditya Pushkarna
Music Label: Saregama
Genre: Hip Hop
Sub-Genre: Rap
Language:Hindi
Country of Origin/Source: India


Follow Kaanphod to know more: 
üëâ Subscribe to KaanPhod : https://www.youtube.com/@KaanPhodMusic 
üëâ Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/kaanphod 
üëâ Follow us on X: https://x.com/kaanphodmusic?s=11 
üëâ Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/kaanphodmusic/ 


Lyrics

Mein jaga jaga jaga Puri raat bhar 
Mein bhaga bhaga bhaga pichhe rakshas
Mein jana chahta waha jaha Shanti 
Gana gana gana gana lagta mujhe shrap ab

Kahani paardarshi sabhi ka istakbal
Kami kitabo ki par school gaya basta daal
Kabhi nahi aa paayi dawayi maa ki time par
Aaj maa ki ek khaasi pe Ghar bana aspataal

Khubiya chhod woh kamiya batake chale gayi
Samjha tha jindagi jindagi samjhakar chale gayi
Bola tha ek gaane pe ek peti utha lunga 
Woh kisi mahine Wale ki tamkhwa par chale gaye 

Na talasha mandiro mein  masjeedo mein 
khoya nahi 
Bandeesho mein hasta tha aur zanzeero mein
Roya nahi
Lanat hai uss bete par jo chori karke moz 
Karta
Baap jiska raat ko chain se kabhi soya nahi 

Naye makaano mein mandir purana yaad kar
Haath jod , aas kar , galtiyo ko maaf kar
Bada Dil , bada Ghar , lambi gehri saans bhar
Zubana mithi unke jinke khoon laga daat par

Bro , mein kehna chahta bhot kuchh 
Mata Peeta bhot khush 
Sannata dekha , roz dukh 
Ata nahi tha likhna ab likhta hoon baate bhot khoob 

Paayi paayi ke vaaste , bhai bhai mein  faasle
High figh si life ni si fi se haadse
Aight side mein but iya mice vice de haat mein
Lime light se door life line yeh art hai 

Baat suni mene Ghar ki chaar 
Toh darkinar ni Kari kalakari 
Padti maar jo jhadti maar ke 
Tapri paar the Farzi chaar 
Todke deeware dhar ki le gaye 
Thaane mein band hua agli baar
Baap ne bola aulad nahi meri 
Fir baap ne chhudaya apki baar 

Chalte show mein ata call 
papa bole kidhar ho
Jaldi aja Ghar pe mujhe 
Parwa nahi tum jidhar ho 
Ab mein jata show pe toh 
Utaar te hai Nazar pehle
Ab Mein chadta stage pe
Check pe 5 figure ho

Yeh saari cheeze ek raat mein ni aayi
Mein so Gaya bhula roti khairat mein nahi  khayi
Tu kalakar accha hai par mann mein tere khot
Warna accho acho ke safalta hath mein nahi ayi

Cheekhu zor se deeware mujhe khaa jayegi 
Chalta Jaa rha sadak pata nahi  kaha jayegi
Aaye din bas jaayedaat ke kagzat pe marpit 
Mein Ghar ka sabse Chhota mere hisse mein toh  maa aayegi

snippet.title: Raj Thackeray Invites Kamiya Jani For A Heartwarming Maharashtrian Sunday Brunch Ep 149 | CurlyTales
snippet.description:
Join me for a special episode of Sunday Brunch as I step into the home of one of Maharashtra‚Äôs most loved politicians, Raj Thackeray, for an authentic Maharashtrian breakfast! Known for his no-nonsense attitude and fiery speeches, Raj Thackeray reveals a completely different side‚Äîchilled out, nostalgic, and full of laughter.

Over a delicious spread of Sabudana Khichdi, Tadpe Poha, Sabudana Vada, Seera, and Batata Thalipeeth, we dive into his personal life, school memories, and his deep bond with the legendary Bala Saheb Thackeray. He shares heartwarming stories about their relationship, his love for Maharashtrian culture, and even some hilarious anecdotes from his younger days.

This episode also features his son, Amit Thackeray, who is stepping into politics and gearing up for the electoral elections in Dadar and Mahim.

Watch as Raj Thackeray's "angry young man" persona takes a backseat to his warm and approachable vibe in this candid, fun-filled conversation. Don‚Äôt forget to like, share, and subscribe for more such unique stories and inspiring personalities!

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta

Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)

Sharad Sankla as Abdul

snippet.description:
Tag Awara Ke (Official Video) Amanraj Gill, Shivani Yadav, Shiva Choudhary | New Haryanvi Song 2024

Nav Haryanvi Presenting "Tag Awara Ke (Official Video)" a New Haryanvi Songs Haryanavi 2024. Sung by Amanraj Gill and Shiva Choudhary. Starring with Shivani Yadav. Lyrics are Penned by Amanraj Gill. Music given by Amanraj Gill. Music Label by Nupur Audio.

Susbscribe  @NavHaryanvi  

#tagawarake #amanrajgill #shivaniyadav #shivachoudhary #navharyanvi #haryanvi #haryanvisong #haryanvisongs #haryanvisongsharyanavi #haryanvigane #newharyanvisong #latestharyanvisong #hrsong #newharyanvisongsharyanavi2024 

Lyrics : 
Oh thare laagale kyon sharey aam ye tag awara ke
Kade pahada mein kade akhada mein ravein dere yaaran ke

Kade pahada mein kade akhada mein ravein dere yaaran ke
Thare 2 number ke kaam nire taqleefaan aale rey


Gaadi ke number pe satte 
Raakhe dass dass gela patthey
Khele zindagi gele satte
Naa kaam shareefaan aale re

Gaadi mein karwa ke hooter
Rakhu gel bithake shooter
Maara raah rokan je chahiye
Jaiye sey chhati mein gaadey rey

Kyun itne masle rakhey
Aatma rakhey kashti mein
Jo khatkhyaa jaan drishti mein
Woh paaya nahi shrishti mein


Jo khatkhyaa jaan drishti mein
Woh paaya nahi shrishti mein
Maare khoon ubaaley taate
Lade jawani aale jaatey

Tadke mare sapate
Chhorey paale chhaley rey

Gaadi ke number pe satte 
Raakhe dass dass gela patthey
Khele zindagi gele satte
Naa kaam shareefaan aale re

Gaadi mein karwa ke hooter
Rakhu gel bithake shooter
Maara raah rokan je chahiye
Jaiye sey chhati mein gaadey rey

Chaale saare ye theke aa tola banau
Kara deve hain saare callan pe kaam
Maahri nyaari hain line ji me laagde na jaam
Kyon leve bhadak le baba ka naam

Rupiya naa rakhte hum locker mein madam
Duniyaa ne mane thokkar pe madam
Hawa mein rehna toh banta hain zindagi mein
Chhattaan pe utre jinke helicopter hain madam

Positive chhora konya tootti smile
Easy schedule rave kaan pe mobile
Maare kharchein ne charche ne parche ne dekh
Khule lokkaan de munh band ho jaa se thaa hi

Tu ravey udatta note yaari mein
Tanne jodyaa ke
Kothiyan car-aan wala dharti ae
Vaas crore-aan ki

Kothiyan car-aan aale dharti ae
Vaas crore-aan ki
Note-aan ki bhar ri almaari
Kade pajero kade safari

Buddhi amne teri anaari
Kadi naa tenta taale rey

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant.
